    "description": {
      "value": "<p>With a scattering of petals, you launch a spear of thorns which wraps around your foes. When you initiate this strike, make a line attack with a range of 5 feet for every 2 initiator levels you possess. Each creature in the line takes your weapon's damage plus an additional 3d6 and is inflicted with [sprout 1]. A successful Reflex save (DC 13 + your initiation modifier) halves the damage and negates the sprout.</p>"
